name: Scan or Scam - Winter Update
summary:
WHAT'S NEW

Christmas! New strange customers are coming, finds the little elves and shot them just to see what happen, you can also choose the music. And of course a lot of presents! 

Your new Boss! Do the tasks he's giving you, make more money.

Leaderboard: be the best (or worst) cashier in town!

A bunch of new items to play with!

Scan, weigh, sell! 🛒
